prompt_text: Describe the best day of your life.
content_text: The best day of my life. This one I became father that which was last month, 27th of September 2023. It was a different feeling altogether. The moment I hold my daughter in my hands, it was a different feeling altogether. It was magical around. I was flying in a blue dream at that point of time. I was like in cloud #9. It was, it was a fake. Probably the best feeling I will ever have in my life. It was beautiful. It was unimaginable.
